":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967309,14,1),(14229,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"752\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Moms at family restaurants.\",\"desc\":\"A part-time worker at a family restaurant, Jiancheng is tormented daily by monster parents. His only solace is \\\"Yuwei Mama.\\\" One day, he accidentally catches Yuwei Mama playing with her child when her skirt unexpectedly rides up, and he cautiously approaches… An adult game filled with the alluring mothers from the restaurant, and a racing heart for Jiancheng, is about to begin!\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2148_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2148_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Moms at family restaurants.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Afterword for Chapter 106\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967334,14,1),(14230,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"2126\",\"title\":\"帝王App\",\"ticai_id\":\"9\",\"tags\":[\"22,44,469,1025,1379,1414,1415,1457\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"整天打游戏的超级废宅-陈子俊意外安装了一个App，人生有了180度大转变。拥有这个神级App就能赚大钱还可以让所有女人爽到上天堂!「有了这个，天底下没有我征服不了的女人了!」\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2126_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2126_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"1\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967368,14,1),(14231,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"730\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Emperor App\",\"desc\":\"A hardcore gamer who spends all day playing games—Chen Zijun—accidentally installed an app that completely changed his life. With this god-level app, he can make a lot of money and send every woman to paradise! “With this, there isn’t a woman in this world I can’t conquer!”\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2126_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2126_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Emperor App\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 90 (Final Episode)\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967390,14,1),(14232,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"2250\",\"title\":\"职场陷阱\\/職場陷阱\",\"ticai_id\":\"1\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"大学时期吃得很开的宇贤，毕业之后踏进职场却尝尽社会冷暖，还被公司同事仙人跳!!受够不公不义的宇贤决定要以其人之道，还治其人之身，并让对方一步步踏进无法自拔的陷阱里…「我会让妳彻底变成我的形状，对我欲罢不能!!」\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2250_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2250_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967461,14,1),(14233,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"851\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Workplace pitfalls \\/ Career traps.\",\"desc\":\"During university, Yu Xian was quite popular, but after graduating and entering the workforce, he experienced the harsh realities of society and was even set up by his colleagues! Having had enough of injustice, Yu Xian decided to fight back using their own methods, leading them down a path of an inescapable trap... \\\"I will completely mold you into my image, making you utterly obsessed with me!!\\\"\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2250_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2250_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Workplace pitfalls.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 87 \\/ Chapter 87\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967484,14,1),(14234,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"2247\",\"title\":\"家政妇小姐姐\",\"ticai_id\":\"6\",\"tags\":[\"12,44,299,1025,1379,1427,1473,1474\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"和15年前同样下着梅雨的初夏夜晚，全身淋得湿答答的邻居姐姐再次出现于家门前，乞求翔平的爸爸收留她们姐妹俩当家庭帮佣。翔平看着对过往只字不提的初恋对象-芷榆姐感觉越来越陌生，而和差不多年纪的芷琳，却在同一个屋檐下愈发亲近...「少爷，请问今天想来点什么♥」\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2247_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2247_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967684,14,1),(14235,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"848\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Maid sister. (Or, more colloquially)Lovely maid.\",\"desc\":\"On a midsummer night, raining as it did 15 years ago during the plum rain season, the neighbor sister, completely soaked, reappeared at their doorstep, begging Shōhei’s father to take her and her sister in as live-in help. Shōhei watched his first love, Zhiyu, feeling increasingly distant as she made no mention of their past, while Zhilin, around his age, grew closer and closer under the same roof… “Young Master, what would you like today? ♥”\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2247_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2247_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Maid sister. (Or, more colloquially)Lovely maid.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 52\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967706,14,1),(14236,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/banner/info.html','{\"id\":\"22\",\"position\":\"1\",\"title\":\"2144\",\"mid\":\"2144\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2144_c_l.jpg\",\"link\":\"\",\"status\":\"1\",\"sort\":\"3\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967781,14,1),(14237,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/banner/save_translation','{\"id\":\"1\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"banner_id\":\"22\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2144_e_l.jpg\"}','118.101.173.199','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1754967795,14,1),(14238,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/banner/info.html','{\"id\":\"25\",\"position\":\"3\",\"title\":\"2148\",\"mid\":\"2148\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/2148_c_l.jpg\",\"link\":\"\",\"status\":\"1\",\"sort\"