 to reach you.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"47th stroke.\"}','58.152.26.156','香港--中西區--中環',1756131992,13,1),(15403,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1724\",\"title\":\"游戏不能这样玩 \\/ 游戏规则我来定 （章节不完整 少95-97话）\",\"ticai_id\":\"1\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"叙述：又菜又爱玩的暴躁女,遇到前职业选手的沈稳男,二人究竟会擦出怎样的火花?\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1724_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1724_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\"}','58.152.26.156','香港--中西區--中環',1756132017,13,1),(15404,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1719\",\"title\":\"难攻不落的女孩是系上最M的变态！？\",\"ticai_id\":\"6\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"漂亮、成绩、时髦都是第一。卞泰英是她所在系的尖子生，周围总是被男生盯着看。但她用都铁甲般地防御将一切弹回来…\\n和她同学科的金南珠与泰英保持友谊并寻找着机会，但泰英却没有给出太多机会。\\n另一方面，与学习无缘的高年级学生、青梅竹马的池宇，想起与泰英和在一起的高中时光时，为了要成功攻略她，告诉他一个令人惊讶的秘密…!?\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1719_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1719_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"en\":{\"title\":\"The seemingly unapproachable girl is the most submissive freak in the department!?\",\"desc\":\"Beautiful, top grades, and trendy – she excels in all areas. Bian Tae-yeong is the star student in her department and constantly has male attention surrounding her. But she deflects everything with an iron-like defense… \\n\\nHer classmate, Kim Nam-joo, maintains a friendship with Tae-yeong and looks for opportunities, but Tae-yeong doesn’t offer many.\\n\\nOn the other hand, Ji Woo, a senior student who isn’t academically inclined and a childhood friend, remembers their high school days with Tae-yeong and, determined to succeed in winning her over, reveals a surprising secret…!?\",\"image\":\"\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"\",\"keyword\":\"The seemingly unapproachable girl is the most submissive freak in the depa