tus\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"[周三更新@禁漫天堂 ] 写玩游戏负评后居然在成人游戏\\\"情爱学园\\\"的世界醒来...游戏制作人强迫我攻略6个女角玩到后宫结局，不然就要杀了我!有够小家子气的...好吧，我只能努力勾引全部六个女孩活到后宫结局了...!\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1579_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1579_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"1\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"en\":{\"title\":\"Do not log out of the school network.\",\"desc\":\"[Wednesday Update @Jinzou Paradise] After writing a negative review for a game, I woke up in the world of the adult game \\\"Love Academy\\\"... The game creator is forcing me to romance six girls to achieve a harem ending, or he\'ll kill me! It\'s so petty... Well, I guess I have no choice but to try my best to seduce all six girls and survive to the harem ending...!\",\"image\":\"\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"\",\"keyword\":\"Do not log out of the school network.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 120                                                                                 120\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481509,13,1),(15597,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"208\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Do not log out of the school network.\",\"desc\":\"[Wednesday Update @Jinzou Paradise] After writing a negative review for a game, I woke up in the world of the adult game \\\"Love Academy\\\"... The game creator is forcing me to romance six girls to achieve a harem ending, or he\'ll kill me! It\'s so petty... Well, I guess I have no choice but to try my best to seduce all six girls and survive to the harem ending...!\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1579_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1579_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Do not log out of the school network.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 120                                                                                 120\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481524,13,1),(15598,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1743\",\"title\":\"小姐  \",\"ticai_id\":\"9\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"其他名称：아씨内容简介：13岁的石头刚被卖为奴仆时，光是看着主人家的小姐都会脸红，不知不觉他已经成年，身体也越来越健壮结实。从小一起长大的素希小姐和同为奴仆的夏荷也越发成熟美丽，他们之间也开始流淌着不知名的紧张与情愫…\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1743_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1743_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"en\":{\"title\":\"Miss.\",\"desc\":\"Other names: A씨\\nSynopsis: When 13-year-old Seok-ju was first sold into servitude, he would blush just looking at his master’s daughter. Unknowingly, time has passed and he\'s come of age, his body growing stronger and more robust. So-hee, who grew up with him, and Ha-ha, a fellow servant, have both blossomed into beautiful young women, and an unfamiliar tension and affection begins to flow between them…\",\"image\":\"\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"\",\"keyword\":\"Miss.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"The 103rd stroke.\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481550,13,1),(15599,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"357\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Miss.\",\"desc\":\"Other names: A씨\\r\\nSynopsis: When 13-year-old Seok-ju was first sold into servitude, he would blush just looking at his master’s daughter. Unknowingly, time has passed and he\'s come of age, his body growing stronger and more robust. So-hee, who grew up with him, and Ha-ha, a fellow servant, have both blossomed into beautiful young women, and an unfamiliar tension and affection begins to flow between them…\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1743_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1743_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Miss.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"The 103rd stroke.\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481563,13,1),(15600,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1593\",\"title\":\"骑乘姿势预备~起!\\/騎乘姿勢預備~起!\",\"ticai_id\":\"1\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"「有在運動的女人…不一樣~」從外縣市重新搬回首爾的文凱，在公園裡回想起與初戀一同騎自行車的回憶，碰巧與她再次相遇，卻在陰錯陽差之下加入了自行車同好會…然而，整個同好會裡，\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1593_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1593_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"1\",\"isjingpin\":\"1\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"en\":{\"title\":\"Mounting position, prepare~! \\/ Get ready to mount~!\",\"desc\":\"Women who exercise…are different~” Wen Kai, having moved back to Seoul from another province, reminisces about cycling with his first love in the park. By chance, they meet again, and through a misunderstanding, he joins a cycling club…However, within the entire club…\",\"image\":\"\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"\",\"keyword\":\"Campus, emotion, sensual.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Final episode - Step by step towards happiness.\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481583,13,1),(15601,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"222\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Mounting position, prepare~! \\/ Get ready to mount~!\",\"desc\":\"Women who exercise…are different~” Wen Kai, having moved back to Seoul from another province, reminisces about cycling with his first love in the park. By chance, they meet again, and through a misunderstanding, he joins a cycling club…However, within the entire club…\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1593_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1593_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Campus, emotion, sensual.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Final episode - Step by step towards happiness.\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481595,13,1),(15602,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1581\",\"title\":\"上流社会～我要成为人生胜利组～   \",\"ticai_id\":\"8\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"憧憬着上流社会的平凡男子·二宫银治邂逅了上流社会的三井美穗后开始渴望一样的生活。美穗的哥哥刻意接近银治说能教他怎么打入上流社会…「你有那个潜力，毕竟你是那个二宫金治的弟弟」\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1581_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1581_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"en\":{\"title\":\"Upper Class – I Want to Be a Life Winner –\",\"desc\":\"Longing for the life of the upper class, the ordinary man Ginji Minamiya encountered Miho Mitsui of high society and began to desire the same lifestyle. Miho’s brother deliberately approached Ginji, saying he could teach him how to enter their world… “You have the potential, after all you are the younger brother of Kinji Minamiya.”\",\"image\":\"\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"\",\"keyword\":\"Upper Class – I Want to Be a Life Winner –\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 50.\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481617,13,1),(15603,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"210\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Upper Class – I Want to Be a Life Winner –\",\"desc\":\"Longing for the life of the upper class, the ordinary man Ginji Minamiya encountered Miho Mitsui of high society and began to desire the same lifestyle. Miho’s brother deliberately approached Ginji, saying he could teach him how to enter their world… “You have the potential, after all you are the younger brother of Kinji Minamiya.”\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1581_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1581_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Upper Class – I Want to Be a Life Winner –\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 50.\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481632,13,1),(15604,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/save_translation','{\"id\":\"355\",\"lang_code\":\"en\",\"title\":\"Fall Story.\",\"desc\":\"Even though he didn’t say a single word, his intense gaze pierced through the narrow door crack, visually undressing me from head to toe, as if he would burst through the door any second. A wave of pleasure washed over my entire body! That was when I began down this path of depravity and ruin, just to seek that incredibly exhilarating thrill…\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1741_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1741_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Fall Story.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 20\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481654,13,1),(15605,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1741\",\"title\":\"堕落物语\",\"ticai_id\":\"1\",\"tags\":[\"22,44,131,242,1025,1379,6457,6458\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"desc\":\"就算对方一句话也没说.但他强烈的眼神穿过那狭窄的门缝.视奸着我全身上下.仿佛下一秒就会闯进家门.令人快感袭卷全身!我就是从那时候开始走上这条堕落沉沦的路.只为寻求那亢奋无比的刺激...\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1741_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1741_c_l.jpg\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"1\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"en\":{\"title\":\"Fall Story.\",\"desc\":\"Even though he didn’t say a single word, his intense gaze pierced through the narrow door crack, visually undressing me from head to toe, as if he would burst through the door any second. A wave of pleasure washed over my entire body! That was when I began down this path of depravity and ruin, just to seek that incredibly exhilarating thrill…\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1741_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1741_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Fall Story.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 20\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481666,13,1),(15606,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/clear.html','[]','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481700,13,1),(15607,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/del.html','{\"id\":\"4096\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1756481707,13,1),(15608,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/login/login.html','{\"username\":\"nuanua\",\"pwd\":\"qweqwe\",\"code\":\"\"}','14.192.213.64','马来西亚--Kuala Lumpur--吉隆坡',1756520729,13,1),(15609,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadm