image\\/banner\\/1539_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1539_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Under the same roof.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"97th stroke\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757325214,13,1),(17497,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1540\",\"ticai_id\":\"1\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"1\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"zh\":{\"title\":\"草药爱谈\",\"desc\":\"幽静的乡村，爷爷世代相传的天然温泉「万岁澡堂」。即将开业，独自负责澡堂运营的「镇浩」唯一的职员邻居姐姐「世静」和男儿将进行大扫除。整理仓库时偶然发现的可疑药草束和药材图鉴。用奇妙的香气浓郁的药材熬制的绿色草药汤让男女之间变得火热…！\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1540_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1540_c_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"草药爱谈\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"第81画\"},\"en\":{\"title\":\"Herbal Talk\\/Herbal Bathhouse\",\"desc\":\"A tranquil countryside setting, and \\\"Manzai Bathhouse,\\\" a natural hot spring passed down through generations by Grandfather. It\'s about to open, and \\\"Machihiko,\\\" solely responsible for running the bathhouse, enlists the help of his neighbor and only employee, older sister \\\"Yoshihiko,\\\" and a young man for a thorough cleaning. While organizing the warehouse, they stumble upon a suspicious bundle of herbs and a medicinal herb compendium. A green herbal soup brewed with mysteriously fragrant, potent ingredients ignites a passionate heat between the two of them…!\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1540_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1540_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Herbal Talk \\/ Discussions about Herbs\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"The 81st stroke.\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757325233,13,1),(17498,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/photos.html','{\"id\":\"86920\",\"lang\":\"en\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757325277,13,1),(17499,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/photos.html','{\"id\":\"86919\",\"lang\":\"en\"}','5