.html','{\"id\":\"1780\",\"ticai_id\":\"1\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"zh\":{\"title\":\"初次深交，请多指教\",\"desc\":\"当道贤正悠闲地在家写作时，眼前突然一片黑，醒来之后发现自己被奇怪的女神召唤，身旁还有一个半裸的陌生女子-晓彤!想不到女神一开口就要他们上床来协助祂拯救无辜生命。道贤与晓彤会愿意救素昧平生的陌生人而献出自己的第一次吗?!「救人要紧，请两位现在马上做爱并获得高潮!」\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1780_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1780_c_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"初次深交，请多指教\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"                                                                                第83话                                                                                                                        83                                                 \"},\"en\":{\"title\":\"It’s a pleasure to meet you and begin this deeper connection; please guide me.\",\"desc\":\"While Dao Xian was leisurely writing at home, darkness suddenly fell before his eyes. When he awoke, he found himself summoned by a strange goddess, with a half-naked stranger – Xiaotong – beside him! He never imagined the goddess would ask them to have sex to help her save innocent lives. Will Dao Xian and Xiaotong be willing to sacrifice their virginity to save complete strangers?! \\\"Saving people is paramount, please both of you have intercourse and reach orgasm immediately!\\\"\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1780_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1780_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Nice to meet you, I look forward to getting to know you better.\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"Episode 83\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757325951,13,1),(17558,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1910\",\"ticai_id\":\"6\",\"tags\":[\"44,1025,1379\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"0\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"zh\":{\"title\":\"我体内的神君 \",\"desc\":\"旅游度假竟被巨屌之神附身?巫女和老板娘主动献上胴体并虔诚的让我肆意索取...！\",\