 Master, come on, get aroused?\",\"desc\":\"Three people working in the AI department of GSA, a large company. Shirō Matsumoto, highly responsible to the point of being afraid to have children, is gradually losing his physical and mental strength as he gets older. Hideaki Kuga, so busy with life that he doesn’t have time for romance, let alone masturbation. Ayane Nakamura, enthusiastic by nature, but has been infected by the coldness of Matsumoto and Kuga after spending every day with them. One day, the three of them were given the opportunity to test their company’s new product… However, they didn’t expect the alpha test product to be artificial intelligence. The three went home as usual. But waiting for them was an artificial intelligence that looked exactly like a human. A 30-day AI alpha test had begun.\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1531_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1531_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Master, would you like to get aroused? \\/ Master, come on, get aroused?\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"The 37th stroke.\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327903,13,1),(17673,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/info.html','{\"id\":\"1531\",\"ticai_id\":\"6\",\"tags\":[\"\"],\"status\":\"1\",\"mhstatus\":\"0\",\"isjingpin\":\"1\",\"issole\":\"0\",\"xianmian\":\"0\",\"translations\":{\"zh\":{\"title\":\"主人，要不要勃起一下呢?\",\"desc\":\"在大公司GSA社的人工智能AI部门工作的三人。松村士郎，责任心很强以至于一直害怕生孩子，随着年龄的增长，身体和精神都渐渐力不从心。古贺英明，忙于生活，别说恋爱，甚至自慰都没时间。中村彩音，性格热情，但每天和松村和古贺待在一起，已经被他们的冷漠传染。突然某一天，三个人都得到了测试自家公司的新产品的机会…然而没有想到进行α测试的产品竟然是人工智能。3人和往常一样正常地下班。迎接他们的，竟然是和人类长得一模一样的人工智能。30天的人工智能α测试就这么开始了。\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1531_c_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1531_c_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"主人，要不要勃起一下呢 \\/ 主人，来勃起吧?\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"第37画\"},\"en\":{\"title\":\"Master, would you like to get aroused? \\/ Master, come on, get aroused?\",\"desc\":\"Three people working in the AI department of GSA, a large company. Shirō Matsumoto, highly responsible to the point of being afraid to have children, is gradually losing his physical and mental strength as he gets older. Hideaki Kuga, so busy with life that he doesn’t have time for romance, let alone masturbation. Ayane Nakamura, enthusiastic by nature, but has been infected by the coldness of Matsumoto and Kuga after spending every day with them. One day, the three of them were given the opportunity to test their company’s new product… However, they didn’t expect the alpha test product to be artificial intelligence. The three went home as usual. But waiting for them was an artificial intelligence that looked exactly like a human. A 30-day AI alpha test had begun.\",\"image\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1531_e_h.jpg\",\"cover_horizontal\":\"notic\\/image\\/banner\\/1531_e_l.jpg\",\"keyword\":\"Master, would you like to get aroused? \\/ Master, come on, get aroused?\",\"last_chapter_title\":\"The 37th stroke.\"}}}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327914,13,1),(17674,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/photos.html','{\"id\":\"87500\",\"lang\":\"en\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327951,13,1),(17675,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/photos.html','{\"id\":\"87501\",\"lang\":\"en\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327957,13,1),(17676,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/chapter_del.html','{\"id\":\"87501\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327963,13,1),(17677,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/chapter_del.html','{\"id\":\"87503\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327978,13,1),(17678,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/chapter_del.html','{\"id\":\"87504\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327983,13,1),(17679,'后台操作 - POST',0,'https://newmaomimhadmin.9xyrp3kg4b86.com/comic/chapter_del.html','{\"id\":\"87505\"}','58.152.46.115','香港--中西區--中環',1757327987,13,1),(17680,'后台操作 - POST',0,